        Makes changes to the return for the user with the given sessionID to the return from the given year and email's user.
        Parameters:
        email - String The email of the user whose tax return is being changed.
        year - int The tax return year of the tax return being changed.
        status - String The status in our system of the tax return that is being updated.
        amount - double The total amount that the customer is required to pay for their tax return.
        sessionID - String The sessionID of the user. In order to update the user, the user with the given sessionID
        Returns:
